## Civilization Evolution

Universe → Consciousness → Civilization → AI → Interstellar Civilization

## Civilization Stability Problem

When technological capability increases faster than governance capacity, civilization instability occurs.

Civilization Stability Engineering aims to prevent civilization collapse during technological transitions.

